title: Salmon Caesar salad
ingredients: ['Salmon', '1 tablespoon coconut sugar', '1 tablespoon smoked paprika', '1 teaspoon grated orange zest', '2 teaspoons dried oregano', '1 teaspoon ground cinnamon', '1/2 teaspoon sea salt', '1 tablespoon olive oil', '3 salmon fillets', 'Caesar Salad', '1 head lettuce, chopped, or as needed', '2 tablespoons apple cider vinegar', '1 tablespoon olive oil', '5 teaspoons spicy mustard', '1 clove garlic, minced', '1 pinch salt', '20g croutons, or to taste']
